org.cpsolver.instructor.model

Class Attribute

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cpsolver.instructor.model.Attribute

  • public class Attribute
extends Object
    Attributes of an instructor. Each instructor can have a number of attributes and there are attribute preferences on teaching requests. Each attribute has an id, a name and a Attribute.Type.
    Version:
